text: Osman Öcalan (1958 – 15 November 2021) was a Turkish Kurdish militant politician He was the commander of the Kurdistan Workers' Party. Öcalan died of COVID-19 on 15 November 2021 in Erbil, Kurdistan Region at the age of 63. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Turkish military people Category:Kurdish activists
title: Osman Öcalan
